<h1>LmComponents Notebook</h1>

<p class="intro">
    Welcome to the LmComponents Notebook - an interactive showcase and testing environment for the LmComponents library.
    This application is specifically designed to be easy to navigate with MCP browser tools and other AI assistants.
</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h2>About LmComponents</h2>
    <p>
        LmComponents is a Blazor component library specifically designed to be easily developed and maintained by
        Large Language Models (LLMs) such as Claude and Gemini. The project emphasizes clear documentation,
        simple navigation, and LLM-friendly tooling.
    </p>
</div>

